
Lake Alhambra is a private ponds pond that was built in the center of the Lake Alhambra Estates housing development in East Davis. Entrance to the development is located at the intersection of Alhambra Drive and Loyola Drive. Like Stonegate Lake, use of the lake is limited to http://lakealhambra.org/lakealhambra/outside_home.asp Lake Alhambra Estates Homeowners Association members only.
